nodes.text: The Secret Weapons (SW) expansion of the Star Wars PocketModel TCG (Trading Card Game) was to have been the next set of the game to be released by WizKids after the interjection of the three Clone Wars animated TV series-based expansions, Clone Wars, Clone Wars Tactics, and Clone Wars Conquest. Scheduled to be released in 2009, it is unclear at this time if the expansion will be distributed after the sale of the gaming company—and the PocketModel trademarked games—by Topps to the National Entertainment Collectors Association (NECA) without the Star Wars brand license.
